                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d1">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign> in red and black on
                      <locus target="#1r #13r #19v #45r" facs="003 015 022 047"/> (erased),
                      <locus target="#60r #64v #76r #93r #97r #107v #114v #122r" facs="062 067 078 095 099 110 117 124"/> (one column);
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign> in black on <locus target="#28r #88r" facs="030 090"/>.
                      A line of alternating red and black dots marks the division between groups of ten psalms (<locus target="#38v" facs="041"/>).
                    A row of full-stop symbols marks divisions in the Praises of Mary (<locus target="#114v #119r #125r" facs="117 121 127"/>).</decoNote>
